import React from 'react';
import { createGlobalStyle } from 'styled-components'

import Header from './elements/Header'
import Home from './Home'

const GlobalStyle = createGlobalStyle`
    body{
        margin: 0
        padding: 0
        box-sizing: border-box
    }
`



const App = () => 
(
<>
    <Header />
    <Home />
    <GlobalStyle />
</>
)

export default App;
